sys_remote_update_set.description:
Service Portal widget which allows to capture user's signatures. The update set contains the following: 1. Service Portal Widget 2. Javascript file which is required for the widget 3. ACL which grants read access to that javascript file (this is requried so the widget functions properly)
Release history: 10-30-2020: restrict submission if there is no signature 3-27-2020: initial release
sys_remote_update_set.name: Signature Pad Widget 1.1
